data.description: Cute, Clean and & Affordable.  This CHARMER has some really great features.  Spacious living room and good sized bedrooms.  The home has a great durable metal roof and central heat and air.   Laminate flooring and a large eat in kitchen.  Xeriscape front yard and a blank canvas in the back.  In close proximity to shopping, banking, and schools.  Don't miss your opportunity to purchase this very AFFORDABLE home.  Call a broker today to schedule your private showing.
